  "body": "<p>I have to admit it's pretty surreal seeing my Project Life spread on <a href=\"http://www.hsn.com/products/project-life-complete-scrapbook-kit-blush-edition-as/7134874\">HSN.com</a>. Thanks to Instagram, I was alerted when <a href=\"http://instagram.com/jasminemarie\">JasmineMarie</a> posted <a href=\"http://instagram.com/p/XRET5Ax6tp/\">this photo</a> with the caption, \"I can't even explain how excited I am right now for #projectlife. Eek! <a href=\"http://instagram.com/amytangerine\">@amytangerine</a> and <a href=\"http://instagram.com/chiaotan\">@chiaotan</a>, I see you on TV!\" So the next thing I had to do was get my tush off the sofa (I suppose I could have just tried turning on the TV), and I went to my computer to see if I could find it online. Lo and behold, it was the first image that popped up on their website. So neat.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/dc5eaef7c6c41275.png?v=1782531711\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Extremely grateful to Becky Higgins for creating this amazing memory keeping system and for the fun opportunity to work with <a href=\"http://www.hsn.com/products/project-life-complete-scrapbook-kit-blush-edition-as/7134874\">the Blush edition</a>. I especially love that it goes so well with <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/_yes_please_/%3Fpp%3D300\">Yes, Please!</a></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/bb922618313d79b0.png?v=1782531714\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>For those of you who have reached out in various ways, THANK YOU for your enthusiasm. And yes, if you chose the auto-ship for either <a href=\"http://www.hsn.com/products/project-life-complete-scrapbook-kit-blush-edition-as/7134874\">Blush</a> or <a href=\"http://www.hsn.com/products/project-life-complete-scrapbook-kit-jade-edition-as/7134873\">Jade</a>, you will be getting the exclusive Amy Tangerine mini kit in September! Woohoo. Yes, this is an exclusive product and will not be available anywhere else. Apparently they are selling quickly. At the time this post went up, over 7550 had sold and there are only 22 hours left. Whoa!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
}